        <mxCell id="fbDC7U7bSzpT1u-7KixK-20" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;-Only one Core can access&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;the CAN bus at once&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;-Therefore access to the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;CAN bus has to be&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;synchronized with a&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;semaphore&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="ellipse;shape=cloud;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1">
